                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220220-158-off857 t18220220-158-cd858"></join>, one pair of pantaloons, value 7 s.; one shirt, value 2 s.; one waistcoat, value 4 s.; one gown skirt, value 2 s.; one pair of gloves, value 6 d., and one neckcloth, value 6 d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18220220-158-victim1492" type="victimName">
